ngs\nare taken to be real at the grand unification scale, the CEDM constraints are\nsatisfied even if $m_{\\tilde t}\\sim 1$ TeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Feb 2017 08:20:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2017 08:17:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 14 Apr 2017 02:55:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 19 Jun 2017 09:26:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-20"}
